OL,11,Fnew look title sequences and associated
OL,12,Fgraphics.
OL,13,
OL,14,FThe 1pm, 6pm and 9pm programmes
OL,15,F(weekdays) and weekend programmes all
OL,16,Fshare the same studio set - which has a
OL,17,Fmaroon/beige colour scheme, in line
OL,18,Fwith the graphics package. David Lowe
OL,19,Fcomposed the new theme tune.
